---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Neon Injector"
  description="Learn how Neon Injector collects, uses, and protects your personal information to ensure a secure and transparent experience."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-8 text-center">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          <p class="mb-6">At Neon Injector, we are committed to protecting your privacy and ensuring a transparent experience. This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect, use, store, and safeguard your personal information when you use our tool or interact with our website. By using Neon Injector, you agree to the practices described below.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We collect minimal data to provide a seamless and personalized experience. The types of information we may collect include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Contact Information</strong>: Your name and email address when you submit inquiries through our <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact</a> form.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: Anonymous data on how you interact with Neon Injector, such as app usage patterns, to improve functionality and user experience.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information</strong>: Technical details like Android OS version, device model, and app version to ensure compatibility and troubleshoot issues.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We use collected information solely to enhance your experience with Neon Injector. Specific uses include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Support and Communication</strong>: To process and respond to your support requests or inquiries submitted via the <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a>.</li>
            <li><strong>App Improvement</strong>: To analyze anonymized usage trends and optimize Neon Injectorâ€™s performance and features.</li>
            <li><strong>Optional Updates</strong>: To send occasional newsletters about new skins, features, or updates, but only if you opt in to receive them.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">3. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">We prioritize your privacy and do not sell or share your personal information with third parties, except in the following cases:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Legal Compliance</strong>: When required by law, court orders, or other legal processes.</li>
            <li><strong>Safety and Rights</strong>: To protect the rights, property, or safety of Neon Injector, its users, or the public.</li>
            <li><strong>Service Providers</strong>: With trusted service providers (e.g., hosting or analytics) who adhere to strict confidentiality agreements and do not retain your data.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">4. Data Security</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">We implement industry-standard security measures, including encryption and secure servers, to protect your data. However, no online system is completely immune to risks. We recommend exercising caution when sharing sensitive information and using secure networks. If you suspect a data breach, contact us immediately at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a>.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">5. Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">You have control over your personal information. Your rights include:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Access</strong>: Request a copy of the personal data we hold about you.</li>
            <li><strong>Deletion</strong>: Request the deletion of your personal data, subject to legal obligations.</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-Out</strong>: Unsubscribe from email communications at any time via the unsubscribe link or by contacting us.</li>
            <li><strong>Raise Concerns</strong>: Contact us via the <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a> or at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a> for any privacy-related issues.</li>
          </ul>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">6. Policy Updates</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">This Privacy Policy was last updated on June 10, 2025. We may update this policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or legal requirements. Updates will be posted on this page, and we encourage you to review it regularly. For questions or concerns, please reach out via our <a href="/contact" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Contact page</a>.</p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>